text: Mishkino () is a rural locality (a village) in Nauruzovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 86 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 65 km from Uchaly, 5 km from Nauruzovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Mishkino, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
